headline: Axon (AXON) Stock Trades Up, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of self defense company AXON (NASDAQ:AXON) jumped 4% in the afternoon session after investment firm TD Cowen reiterated its 'Buy' rating and $925 price target on the stock, citing confidence in the company's growth prospects.
